{"tid":210593,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣候機室眾生相","createTime":"2017-04-21T05:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T08:26:11.000Z","uid":64734,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5384684886915ab151951ec16bf6b15326f99863","tid":210593,"uid":64734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:22:53.000Z","msg":"香港人去到邊都係咁失禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n岩岩係台灣機場等上機，<br />\n成個候機室都會好嘈嘅香港人同細路，<br />\n呀爸呀媽就係到買野，<br />\nD細路跑黎跑去、扔野、大叫，完全冇人理<br />\n同場仲有一大堆人高談闊論<br />\n<br />\n反觀同場嘅台灣人全部都係細細聲講野，或者靜靜地睇書，<br />\n去左咁多日台灣，坐巴士同鐵路都好靜，去到景點又唔會嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩者真係冇得比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4f7b6ab9f8f011505021876767f94c7a9b1ddb","tid":210593,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:25:38.000Z","msg":"不要吹奏 thx"},{"pid":"c5dcf6a885cdf468a6262d08605ed7683b52aa06","tid":210593,"uid":89861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:28:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不要吹奏 thx</blockquote><br />\n香港人不嬲嘈～ 但又以為香港人好有文化，教養"},{"pid":"ef2e7ebec586573d46a7fbd9ffed0ae545d0792e","tid":210593,"uid":64734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:30:43.000Z","msg":"一陣上機可能仲嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb7b33d275e76fa7299f182fd5857f2dbdc98880","tid":210593,"uid":30461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:32:59.000Z","msg":"香港人不嬲都係咁"},{"pid":"09a298adf91c28546e02ced57df44c07cfd20537","tid":210593,"uid":64734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:36:06.000Z","msg":"有冇方法可以令香港人醒覺自己其實好冇品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"123d7c2d